Visualization and Insights:
Create a scatter plot to display station usage patterns in relation to geographic location and time of day.
Analyze scatter plot for trends and insights.
This concise plan outlines the steps to explore bike station usage patterns based on location and time.

The considerable increase in starting riders between 12 PM and 12 AM, compared to the period from 12 AM to 12 PM,
presents an opportunity for businesses to optimize services based on these usage trends. 
